## RESEARCH OBJECTIVE

You are conducting deep background research to support an ongoing real-time geopolitical intelligence analysis of the 2026 Iran-US war. The analysis operates under a framework called GEOPOLITICA that tracks the conflict across military, diplomatic, economic, information, and financial dimensions simultaneously.

The purpose of this research is NOT to summarize what has happened. We have extensive real-time coverage of events. The purpose is to fill specific intelligence gaps that limit our predictive accuracy — the things we don't know that we should know, the options that exist but haven't been deployed yet, the historical patterns that would help us anticipate rather than react.

**Organize your findings under each numbered section below. Be exhaustive. Prioritize information that has predictive value — things that help us anticipate what comes next rather than just describing what already happened.**

